<h6 class="mb-3">Work for Trade – How It Works</h6>
<div class="mb-3">
    <h6>What I Accept:</h6>
    <ul class="list-unstyled mt-2 mb-3">
        <li>Professional Skills (design, writing, marketing, etc.)</li>
        <li>Technical Equipment & Hardware</li>
        <li>Premium Software Licenses</li>
        <li>Educational Resources & Courses</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<h6 class="ff-consolas mb-2">Barter Process:</h6>
<div class="barter-steps">
    <div class="barter-step mb-2">
        <strong class="fw-semibold">1. Initial Proposal</strong>
        <div class="small text-start ms-2 mt-1">
            Contact me with details about your web development needs and what you're offering in exchange.
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="barter-step mb-2">
        <strong class="fw-semibold">2. Value Assessment</strong>
        <div class="small text-start ms-2 mt-1">
            We'll discuss the fair market value of both my services and your offered goods/services to ensure an equitable exchange.
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="barter-step mb-2">
        <strong class="fw-semibold">3. Agreement Terms</strong>
        <div class="small text-start ms-2 mt-1">
            Once we agree on the exchange value, we'll create a simple written agreement outlining deliverables from both sides.
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="barter-step">
        <strong class="fw-semibold">4. Exchange Timeline</strong>
        <div class="small text-start ms-2 mt-1">
            We'll establish milestones for both parties to deliver their part of the agreement, ensuring a fair and transparent process.
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="mt-3 text-center">
    <em class="small">Please note: I reserve the right to decline barter offers that don't match my current needs or value expectations.</em>
</div>